    <svcproc svcproctype="pm" graphiccount="0">
        <title>LUBRICATION</title>
        <para>The steering column universal joints should be lubricated at assembly and as specified in the GROUP 10 -
            LUBRICATION in the CTS-5000 Master Service Manual. Lubricate with Fleetrite EP2 moly grease or equivalent
            NLGI #2 multi-purpose lithium grease.
        </para>
